@startuml
title Review-First Agent Workflow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "User" as User
participant "AI Client\n(planning only)" as Ai
participant "CLI\nagent-plan" as PlanCli
participant "agent.py\nplan_agent_request" as PlanAgent
participant "Safe Profiling\nCSV / folder / profile" as Profiling
participant "Spec Planner\nDatasetProfile -> DatasetSpec" as SpecPlanner
database "Agent Workspace\nagent_request.json\nagent_plan.json\nprofile.json\ndataset_spec.yaml" as Workspace
participant "CLI\nagent-approve" as ApproveCli
participant "agent.py\napprove_agent_workspace" as ApproveAgent
participant "Synthetic Generator\nseeded deterministic" as Generator
participant "Safety Checks\nPII + source-row reuse" as Safety
participant "Validation Core\nschema / relationships /\nconstraints" as Validation
database "Generated Bundle\ngenerated/*\ngeneration_manifest.json\nvalidation_report.json" as Bundle

User -> Ai : asks for synthetic data
Ai -> PlanCli : source, source type,\nworkspace, count, seed, format
PlanCli -> PlanAgent : AgentRequest
PlanAgent -> Profiling : build safe profile
Profiling --> PlanAgent : DatasetProfile\nsafe metadata only
PlanAgent -> SpecPlanner : infer reviewable spec
SpecPlanner --> PlanAgent : DatasetSpec
PlanAgent -> Workspace : write request, plan,\nprofile, spec
PlanAgent --> Ai : awaiting_approval\nartifact paths
Ai --> User : summarize spec\nask for approval

User -> Workspace : review or edit\ndataset_spec.yaml
User -> ApproveCli : approve workspace
ApproveCli -> ApproveAgent : workspace path
ApproveAgent -> Workspace : load reviewed request,\nprofile, DatasetSpec
ApproveAgent -> Generator : generate rows\nfrom spec + seed
Generator --> ApproveAgent : synthetic rows
ApproveAgent -> Safety : verify no source rows copied\nwhen CSV source exists
Safety --> ApproveAgent : safety ok
ApproveAgent -> Validation : validate generated bundle
Validation --> ApproveAgent : validation report
ApproveAgent -> Bundle : write synthetic files,\nmanifest, reports
ApproveAgent --> User : completed result\npaths, seed, row counts

note right of Ai
The AI client plans and explains.
It does not generate rows, validate by
free-form reasoning, or expose raw PII.
end note

note bottom of Workspace
The workspace is the handoff contract:
reviewable spec first, generation only
after explicit approval.
end note

@enduml
